            <title>[SOLR-13972] Insecure Solr should generate startup warning</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-13972</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Warning to the effect of, start Solr with: &quot;solr auth enable -credentials solr:foo -blockUnknown true&#8221; (or some other way to achieve the same effect) if you want to expose this Solr instance directly to users. Maybe the link to the ref guide discussing all this might be in good measure here.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
